text: The Vänersborg Church () is a church building in the central parts of Vänersborg, Sweden. Belonging to the Vänersborg and Väne-Ryr Parish of the Church of Sweden, it was opened in 1784. ==References== ==External links== Category:1784 establishments in Sweden Category:18th-century Church of Sweden church buildings Category:Churches in Västra Götaland County Category:Churches completed in 1784 Category:Vänersborg Category:Churches in the Diocese of Skara
